nodes.text: After the Yuuzhan Vong War began in 25 ABY, the Magnus, or ruler of the planet O'reen and its native species, took a wait-and-see approach to the galaxy-spanning conflict. On the one hand, the Magnus saw the war as an opportunity to spread O'reen's influence beyond the Unknown Regions. On the other, the ruler was wary of drawing unwanted attention from the warring factions. Nevertheless, all records of O'reen were lost to the New Republic, one side of the war, after the Battle of Coruscant.
